CatDescriptText: Players include Della Williams in the first row; from left to right in the back row, the second woman is Tish Burnell, the fourth is Chunky Manns, and the fifth is Ruth Chance.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women softball players wearing uniforms with airplane insignia and "J" on caps, including Tish Burnell, Chunky Manns, Ruth Chance, and Della Williams, with four men in back row, on Kennard Field with Terrace Village in background
